    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You release chakra throughout your body, enhancing your physicality temporarily. This self enhancement reinforces your hands and feet allowing you to break previously inconceivable structures and materials with strikes alone.</p><p>When this jutsu is cast, you must spend 10 chakra, then an additional +5 chakra for every additional round you want this jutsu active beyond the first, up to a maximum of 10 rounds (1 minute).</p><p>While gaining the benefits of this jutsu, you gain +7 DR (Damage reduction) vs B/P/S, +2d6 bonus to melee unarmed/weapon, Taijutsu &amp; Bukijutsu damage rolls twice per turn &amp; deal double damage to objects, structures and constructs.</p>",
